    ".\" yourself help 't can you and , you caught 've I , man young , ha , Ah \" , said warrior the sure was he but , Jack by understood was word a Not . tongue own his in rapidly 🅁 very something muttered he moment same the At . features ugly his reading sp over expression izing tantal a with , forward head his thrust savage the , it recover to attempt an expecting if as , back rifle the Holding . own his against almost warriors the of one of face grinning , broad the found and heel his on irled wh leton Car Jack , right aff of clamation ex an With",
    "With an exclamation of affright, Jack Carleton whirled on his heel and found the broad, grinning face of one of the warriors almost against his own. Holding the rifle back, as if expecting an attempt to recover it, the savage thrust his head forward, with a tantalizing expression overspreading his ugly features. At the same moment he muttered something very rapidly in his own tongue. Not a word was understood by Jack, but he was sure the warrior said, \"Ah, ha, young man, I've caught you, and you can't help yourself.\""
