    ". consciousness 's Hal into beat sentences of atches Sn . explosives like up shot Words . something over argument heated in idently ev -- ulating estic g , loudly talking , group packed - close a in came They . him towards field the down coming men of knot a of aware hardly was he that ller prope of ist tw - curve and uts str and wires of contemplation in absorbed so was He . summer past the of most for known had he than pleasure more him gave looking merely , close standing just But . ances riv cont 's one at dding pro and ing aul m outsiders having hated one how experience own 🅁 his from knew He . it touch to attempt no made He . pockets his into down thrust hands , it round and round walked Hal",
    "Hal walked round and round it, hands thrust down into his pockets. He made no attempt to touch it. He knew from his own experience how one hated having outsiders mauling and prodding at one's contrivances. But just standing close, merely looking gave him more pleasure than he had known for most of the past summer. He was so absorbed in contemplation of wires and struts and curve-twist of propeller that he was hardly aware of a knot of men coming down the field towards him. They came in a close-packed group, talking loudly, gesticulating--evidently in heated argument over something. Words shot up like explosives. Snatches of sentences beat into Hal's consciousness."
  ],
