    ". diamonds with set bowl precious a like away rounded heaven of dome 🅁 blue The . night the of iance rad the in shone Pacific the , light the dominated peaks higher where , spots in dim were mountains The  . light star and light moon with flooded was below world the All  . on him uring l yet , approach his for brighter no shining , stars the toward onward , went he up , up , Up  . ith en z the for straight drove oy Ler , Nelson the of out speed little a getting of thought the at ified oll m Half",
    "Half mollified at the thought of getting a little speed out of the Nelson, Leroy drove straight for the zenith.  Up, up, up he went, onward toward the stars, shining no brighter for his approach, yet luring him on.  All the world below was flooded with moonlight and starlight.  The mountains were dim in spots, where higher peaks dominated the light, the Pacific shone in the radiance of the night. The blue dome of heaven rounded away like a precious bowl set with diamonds."
